- "seeds" metaphorically refers to models;
- "sowers of knowledge" metaphorically refers to users with the role "researcher";
- "garden of innovation" metaphorically refers to the collection of models.

- "creations" refers to models in the context of the database;
- "designers" are the users who created the models;
- The identity of a designer is represented by their full name.

sql:
SELECT M.model_name, U.user_name
FROM models AS M
INNER JOIN users AS U ON M.created_by = U.user_id;

SELECT m.model_id, m.model_name, m.model_version, u.user_name AS created_by
FROM models m
JOIN users u ON m.created_by = u.user_id;

